<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #f3f6fb;
        --card: #ffffff;
        --text: #16202a;
        --muted: #607080;
        --success: #0f7b42;
        --success-bg: #ebf8f1;
        --error: #a12b2b;
        --error-bg: #fff2f2;
        --border: #d9e2ec;
        --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.10);
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB",
          "Microsoft YaHei", "Noto Sans CJK SC", sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(73, 142, 255, 0.14), transparent 34%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(15, 123, 66, 0.12), transparent 28%),
          var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 28px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 760px;
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 28px 32px 18px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .badge.success {
        color: var(--success);
        background: var(--success-bg);
      }

      .badge.error {
        color: var(--error);
        background: var(--error-bg);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 16px 0 8px;
        font-size: 32px;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .summary {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .content {
        padding: 24px 32px 32px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .panel {
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 18px 20px;
        background: #fbfdff;
      }

      .panel h2 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .list {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }

      .list li + li {
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .meta {
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .meta-row {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .meta-label {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .meta-value {
        font-size: 15px;
        word-break: break-all;
      }

      .tip {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="card">
      <section class="hero">
        {{#if success}}
          <div class="badge success">已授权成功</div>
          <h1>{{title}}</h1>
          <p class="summary">Feishu 用户授权已完成。你现在可以回到飞书继续刚才的任务，OpenClaw 将优先使用这次授权建立的 user-scope 能力。</p>
        {{else}}
          <div class="badge error">授权未完成</div>
          <h1>{{title}}</h1>
          <p class="summary">这次授权没有成功落地。回到飞书后，请重新发起授权，或检查应用回调地址、权限范围和网络连通性。</p>
        {{/if}}
      </section>

      <section class="content">
        {{#if success}}
          <section class="panel">
            <h2>当前状态</h2>
            <div class="meta">
              <div class="meta-row">
                <span class="meta-label">授权用户</span>
                <span class="meta-value">{{userOpenId}}</span>
              </div>
              {{#if returnContext}}
                <div class="meta-row">
                  <span class="meta-label">返回上下文</span>
                  <span class="meta-value">{{returnContext}}</span>
                </div>
              {{/if}}
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="panel">
            <h2>接下来怎么做</h2>
            <ol class="list">
              <li>返回飞书，继续你刚才触发的 user-scope 任务。</li>
              <li>如果任务仍提示缺少授权，请直接重试一次，让 OpenClaw 重新检查 token 状态。</li>
              <li>如后续提示 token 失效或需要重新授权，再重新打开授权链接即可。</li>
            </ol>
          </section>

          <p class="tip">提示：本页面只负责完成授权闭环，不会展示敏感 token 内容。</p>
        {{else}}
          <section class="panel">
            <h2>建议检查</h2>
            <ol class="list">
              <li>确认飞书开放平台中已配置正确的回调地址。</li>
              <li>确认授权范围已包含当前任务需要的 user-scope 权限。</li>
              <li>返回飞书重新生成授权链接，再次尝试。</li>
            </ol>
          </section>
        {{/if}}
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
